headline: Teledyne to Hold Investor Meetings
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., March 17, 2025--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) today announced that Edwin Roks, Chief Executive Officer, and Jason VanWees, Vice Chairman, will be holding investor meetings at the Bank of America Global Industrials Conference 2025 on Wednesday, March 19.
